People nowadays are talking about whether teenagers should make decisions by themselves or with other people. Some argue that teenagers should make a choice with other people involved. I firmly believe that making decisions themselves is a better choice. This essay will demonstrate this through studying and fashionable clothing.

First and foremost, choosing which subject to study is one of the most important decisions in a person's academic career, should be decided by the teenagers themselves. This is because teenagers mostly know what they want and they have the right to pursue their dreams. It can be computer science, learning AI, medicine, and all kinds of stuff. If the teenagers had listened to others advice instead of their own hearts, they would have probably lost the life they want

Another important consideration is about dressing clothes. Teenagers should purchase or choose the clothes they want to wear. It could be because of fashion, formal meetings, or school. This will cause possible in no characteristics, with only hearing others' advice.

Admittedly, people might contend that a teenager is not mature enough to make decisions. But they overlook that a teenager nowadays is already mature enough to make life-changing decisions.

In conclusion, although concerns about immature, I maintain that teenagers should make their own decisions, for either studying or fashion.